OL,3,CFarmers fear being 'scapegoated' as
OL,4,Cthe Welsh Government pledges #1
OL,5,Cmillion to tackle climate change
OL,7,FFarmers in Wales have claimed they
OL,8,Fare being made "scapegoats" of the
OL,9,Fclimate change battle as the Welsh
OL,10,FGovernment announced #1 million in
OL,11,Ffunding to help them reduce ammonia
OL,12,Femissions from livestock.
OL,14,FThe Welsh Government says it hopes
OL,15,Fthe funding will "lessen the harmful
OL,16,Fimpacts of the pollutant on the land
OL,17,Fand in the atmosphere".
OL,19,FHowever, high levels of ammonia
OL,20,Femissions have been attributed to the
OL,21,Fcattle industry in particular.
